\\\"}]}\"}, {\"type\": \"text\", \"text\": \"Implemented comprehensive Scala tests in:\\n\\n`tests/src/com.github.ghik/silencer-lib_2.13/1.4.1/src/test/scala/com_github_ghik/silencer_lib_2_13/Silencer_lib_2_13Test.scala`\\n\\nThe new tests cover:\\n- Both public `silent` constructors.\\n- Use through the `scala.annotation.Annotation` contract.\\n- Annotation placement on classes, objects, fields, methods, parameters, local values/functions, type aliases, and generic case classes.\\n- Runtime behavior of annotated code without reflection, serialization, dynamic loading, or Native Image skips.\\n\\nNo build files were changed, and I did not compile or run the tests.\", \"textSignature\": \"{\\\"v\\\":1,\\\"id\\\":\\\"msg_000f7dcbd5a5e45c0169f3ddcec2a48193aab20b50de37d0b7\\\",\\\"phase\\\":\\\"final_answer\\\"}\"}], \"api\": \"openai-responses\", \"provider\": \"OCA\", \"model\": \"gpt-5.5\", \"usage\": {\"input\": 1374, \"output\": 664, \"cacheRead\": 24576, \"cacheWrite\": 0, \"totalTokens\": 26614, \"cost\": {\"input\": 0, \"output\": 0, \"cacheRead\": 0, \"cacheWrite\": 0, \"total\": 0}}, \"stopReason\": \"stop\", \"timestamp\": 1777589699329, \"responseId\": \"resp_000f7dcbd5a5e45c0169f3ddc3cabc819380411741d0d4f5ca\"}, \"toolResults\": []}\n[recv] agent_end\n[send] get_state\n[recv] get_state success\n  sessionFile: ../../../../../../../../.pi/agent/sessions/--home-vjovanov-c-forge-forge4-graalvm-reachability-metadata-forge-local_repositories-forge_worktrees-3628-4802511f--/2026-04-30T22-53-38-814Z_019de099-087e-76c3-a336-d15c17bd7fef.jsonl\n  sessionId: 019de099-087e-76c3-a336-d15c17bd7fef\n[send] get_session_stats\n[recv] get_session_stats success\n  tokens: input=45904 output=5382 cacheRead=184320 cacheWrite=0 total=235606\n\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
